Name: Gold Drill
About the game: Introduction Gold Drill is a classic arcade puzzle game where you connect pipes Clear the stage and enjoy the rewards the girls give you! How to play the game It is cleared by connecting from the start point to the end point with the provided block. Unique blocks can help or hinder your play If the game is difficult, refer to the hint Enjoy your joy by earning rewarded videos! Key Features 3 girl friends embodied in 3D 30 stages filled with blocks with unique characteristics Extreme fun, challenge mode + 30 stages 30 adult video records given as rewards An emergency mode that will protect you from your mother and sister!
